    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《别惊醒野兽》是一款类Rogue潜行游戏，你将扮演一名宝藏猎人，在随机生成的地牢中潜行，躲避强大的野兽，夺取它们的宝藏。然而通往宝藏的道路危机四伏。每个地点由三层关卡构成，遍布敌人、陷阱与环境谜题，需要你巧妙利用抓钩开辟新路径同时躲避威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/a92f27d189fecb530e16e166cab189b8.poster.avif?t=1765221156\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/a92f27d189fecb530e16e166cab189b8.webm?t=1765221156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/a92f27d189fecb530e16e166cab189b8.mp4?t=1765221156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《别惊醒野兽》中，风险与收益的平衡至关重要。冒险过程中你可以收集各种贵重物品，但要小心——每件物品都会增加重量并产生噪音，从而引来敌人的注意，让逃脱更加困难。你将探索四个独特的生态环境，每个区域都有不同的机制与挑战，准备好迎接变化无常的威胁吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/2d2aef733e6eb7a887c4b91c81d67129.poster.avif?t=1765221156\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/2d2aef733e6eb7a887c4b91c81d67129.webm?t=1765221156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/2d2aef733e6eb7a887c4b91c81d67129.mp4?t=1765221156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在成功偷走地窖的主宝物后，你必须沿着原路逃回，但这一次，路径上会布满新的陷阱和障碍，为你的逃生之路增添紧张刺激的挑战。<br><br>你能否在野兽追上你之前带着战利品成功逃脱？每一次闯关都会积累经验，而赚取的金钱可用于升级角色与装备，为下一次冒险带来更多优势。《别惊醒野兽》融合了动态潜行玩法、解谜元素与惊险挑战，确保每一次体验都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/0d6d2a4658383232d8679c259b069441.poster.avif?t=1765221156\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/0d6d2a4658383232d8679c259b069441.webm?t=1765221156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258580/extras/0d6d2a4658383232d8679c259b069441.mp4?t=1765221156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态风险/收益玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每件宝物都会增加财富，但同时增加重量与噪音，让逃脱更加艰难。每一个选择都至关重要——你会冒险争取终极宝藏吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抓钩机制：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用可靠的抓钩与环境互动、解决谜题并避开陷阱。这一独特工具让你能够随心所欲探索程序生成的地牢，并以惊险方式甩开敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>紧张刺激的夺宝脱逃：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你偷走主要宝藏后，必须沿原路返回——但这一次，新的陷阱与危险已布满返回的路。每一次逃跑都是一场惊心动魄的生死竞速。</p></li></ul>",
